    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Slayer Technique:</strong> 11th level</em></p>\n<p>When you score a critical hit or reduce a creature to 0 hit points on your turn, you can use your bonus action to force one creature of your choice that you can see within 30 feet of you to make a Wisdom saving throw against your tech save DC. On a failed save, a creature becomes frightened of you for 1 minute. At the end of each of the creature's turns it repeats this saving throw, ending the effect on a success.</p>",
